### Bug: Sidebar Expand/Collapse Icons Display Incorrectly

<!-- **Medium Severity** -->

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
The `MacOSSidebar` incorrectly uses the `flatIndex` when checking the `_e=
xpandedIndices` set in `_buildAwesomeSidebarItem` and `_buildSidebarItem`=
. Since `_expandedIndices` stores `originalIndex`, this mismatch causes t=
he expand/collapse icons to display the wrong state and prevents expandab=
le items from toggling correctly.
